description.narrative: During 2019, WCARO supported 24 COs, at various stages of the country programming cycle, to develop high quality programming and fostered convergence of the UNICEF presence in the region towards the Key Results for Children as the strategic contribution of WCAR towards the Strategic Plan 2018-2021. Improvements to quality of country programming documentation and reporting including through integration of the KRCs, strengthening RBM capacity and culture, integration of resilience and risk responsiveness, and engagement in UNDS coordination and reform, helped to establish a solid foundation from which COs are better positioned to deliver effective, relevant and sustainable results for children. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
